      <title>《有限与无限的游戏》</title>
      <link>https://rosefinch-midsummer.github.io/zh/posts/book/%E6%9C%89%E9%99%90%E4%B8%8E%E6%97%A0%E9%99%90%E7%9A%84%E6%B8%B8%E6%88%8F/</link>
